file1.highlighted_code: def snt(n): if n < 2: return False for i in range(2, int(n ** 0.5) + 1): if n % i == 0: return False return True def check1(n): for p in range(2, int(n ** 0.5) + 1): if n % p == 0: q = n // p if p!=q and snt(p) and snt(q): return True return False def check2(k, n): if snt(k) and k**8 <= n: return True return False n = int(input()) count = 0 for i in range(2, int(n**0.5) + 1): if check1(i) or check2(i, n): count += 1 print(count)

file2.highlighted_code: def is_prime(n): if n < 2: return False for i in range(2,int(n**0.5)+1): if n % i == 0: return False return True def multiple(n): for k in range(2,int(n**0.5)+1): if n % k == 0 and is_prime(k): new_k = n // k if is_prime(new_k) and new_k != k: return True return False n = int(input()) counter = 0 for i in range(2,int(n**0.5)+1): if multiple(i): counter += 1 i = 2 while i**8 <= n: if is_prime(i): counter += 1 i += 1 print(counter)
